Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.50,0:21:43.77,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.92,0:21:50.61,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.89,0:21:59.28,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.44,0:22:03.54,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.41,0:22:11.84,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.04,0:22:16.26,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.75,0:22:24.35,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.59,0:22:28.81,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.14,0:22:36.36,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.52,0:22:43.33,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.78,0:22:48.87,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.03,0:22:57.93,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.56,0:00:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件仍然與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.76,0:00:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事牽涉到三兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.57,0:00:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,層層隱情引發連串的謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.51,0:00:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.68,0:00:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.13,0:01:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀田三兄弟殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.40,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.37,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽他們說是大案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才特地跑到這種鳥不拉屎的地方來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下這案子不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.41,0:01:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸這麼有名的大偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.18,0:01:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能幫別人找條失蹤的狗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是最適合你了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我的車子故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻煩你送我去前面的那棟別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會好好地答謝你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 我很樂意幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.55,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓堀田 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀…堀田重工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大企業的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.09,0:02:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子在半路上出故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這幾位送我回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這棟別墅的管家敝姓山內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位送我們社長回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人總會遇到困難的 應該互相幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一他們幾個到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看老爺這麼晚了還沒到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在為您擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概巴不得我出車禍早點死掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上正好是我的生日派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.71,0:03:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我招待你們幾位當作是答謝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我們約好的時間 爸爸還沒到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還以為你在路上出了意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好爸爸沒碰上什麼事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在最希望的就是爸爸能夠好好保重身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shator PETRUS 1979年的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是浩一少爺特別為老爺準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那紅酒很高級嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是可以讓人的眼球都掉出來的高檔貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種極品酒可稱得上是紅酒中的帝王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們祝爸爸58歲生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看大哥你先喝一口比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是裡面有毒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就不太好了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太沒禮貌了吧 良二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了 我早就聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥因為他明顯的幼稚做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓爸爸的海外事業受到很大的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.79,0:05:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來是爸爸一聲令下解除了他的董事資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派他到分公司去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我會為了這個而殺害爸爸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近聽說你沉迷於賭場裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還向外面借了一大筆錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天的晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩兄弟還是像以前一樣相親相愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.69,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這就是你的待客之道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己發請帖請我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早在5年前就斷絕父女關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能給妳請帖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想看到妳這張臉 給我滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話要跟我講的人是爸爸你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳沒什麼好講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚本來應該有頓大餐吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.04,0:06:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀田先生跟文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前發生過什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.65,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這裡來當管家也才不過是這兩年的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事情我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威士忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰送我的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發…發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炸彈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子事先被人安裝了炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.11,0:07:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不准進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警方到達之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們都在外面等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在囂張什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算哪根蔥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.01,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是天下第一的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這是黃色炸藥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是黃色炸藥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒聞到火藥的味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭小子怎麼又隨便跑進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手上都是玻璃酒瓶的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威士忌包裝外殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.76,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些刺進身體裡的碎玻璃就是酒瓶的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈一定是裝在這個威士忌的包裝盒內的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以堀田先生的身上才會有這麼多的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不用你來提醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也會發現這一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會出現在房間裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.84,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這裡的電話打不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說我們之中唯一對爸爸懷恨在心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子 就是妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.04,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是5年前就離開這個家了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏會選在今天晚上突然不請自來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想都太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.40,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確到現在還很恨那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨到我想親手殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這件事不是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不知道這是誰做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還真是感謝這個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥們不是也一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是什麼兄妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話線查得怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話線好像全部被人用刀子切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 現在該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.48,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那炸彈是被裝在威士忌的包裝盒裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個盒子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是對它有印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.22,0:09:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把話說清楚好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到良二少爺送給老爺的禮物就是用這個盒子裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是他交給我拿到老爺房間去的所以我有印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是良二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話良二他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.09,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛就是良二少爺的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的車子放在這裡沒開走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見一定還沒走遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還在這附近出沒是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪胎被人戳破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.97,0:10:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的辦法就是坐車先離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的輪胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部被人戳破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人的車都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.28,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就沒有辦法離開這棟別墅了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是良二幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把刀子上面還沾有輪胎的橡膠碎屑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆是怎麼到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都不會開車 是坐車來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一輛就是我開的那一輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前幾天壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還沒法使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果良二先生是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼要把自己的輪胎也戳破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方要是來調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現只有他的輪胎沒有破的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是第一個被懷疑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.11,0:11:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不需要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己送的威士忌爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又一下子不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是一樣會遭到警方的懷疑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以兇手不會是良二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果兇手的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要讓大家都被困在別墅裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一定還會有事情發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.36,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良二先生一定還在這附近出沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家最好集中在一起 不要各自分開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要回我的房間去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也快點回屋裡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.29,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去試試看能否把我的車子修好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你千萬要提高警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐的項鏈墜子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.97,0:12:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.81,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是在找這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說這條項鏈是我現在最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.13,0:12:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是5年前自殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.35,0:12:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是被人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被堀田耕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會離家出走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒辦法原諒我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你一個小孩子說這些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也挽回不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐對堀田先生一直懷恨在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.67,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在威士忌的包裝盒裡裝炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐她有這個機會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.25,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化學肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那炸彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有硫磺和化學藥品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有剛才的化學肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就錯不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手一定就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.75,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子真的好舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我自己設計出來的第一輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是車子的設計師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 5年前我還是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那件事之後我就不幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看到這樣子的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子這麼舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面卻有安全氣囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你能不能幫我把文子小姐叫過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.41,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她去找警方來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果毛利先生離開去叫警方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人都會很不安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裡的管家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有責任留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.01,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定在這附近亂晃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去找柯南好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.64,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片沒什麼好害怕的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是放在你房間裡的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到我的房間去過是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.25,0:15:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒經過我允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在那裡發現了有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你的櫃子裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現你藏著硫磺還有化學藥品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是什麼黃色炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是利用化學肥料和硫磺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再配上一些化學藥品混合製成的手工炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西能做炸彈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按照一定的比例混合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.73,0:15:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所做出來的手工炸彈的威力可不在黃色炸藥之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.27,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.75,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了什麼非要把老爺給殺了不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你為了照片中的人所進行的復仇行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前 他因為堀田先生的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼到最後自殺身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.09,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的親生兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收下良二先生帶來的威士忌之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它送到堀田先生房間的人是山內先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你用磷酸肥料和硫磺這些化學藥品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作的爆炸物裝進酒的包裝盒裡面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盒子的背面裝了引爆物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.02,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把容易揮發的磷酸肥料混到爆炸物裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.33,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有火柴頭大小的用量就可以讓它著火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不是你整項完美犯罪計畫的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.94,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了下一宗犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.51,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須盡可能地讓別人免除對你不必要的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一宗犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子健太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時只是一個默默無聞彈鋼琴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候他已經有一個交往了很久的女朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直沒有穩定的收入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他始終沒辦法向那個女孩子求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在5年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在一場比賽裡得到優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也使得他的才能得到了專家們的肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.99,0:17:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是健太郎他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於向這個女孩子提出結婚的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對這門親事的那個女孩子的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是堀田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個女孩子就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.93,0:17:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太郎為了得到結婚的許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定親自去見堀田先生一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.20,0:17:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀田先生非但沒有答應他們的婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把健太郎的手指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太郎一直把彈鋼琴視為他的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻被永遠地剝奪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.57,0:17:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拋棄了失意的健太郎狠心地走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那可憐的孩子就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我是在健太郎的葬禮上才知道整個事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我根本就不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個普通的上班族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我兒子的事情一點也不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就開始決定復仇了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.06,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把原來的工作辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了等復仇的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就隱姓埋名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當起了這棟別墅的管家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到文子小姐卻已經離家出走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找她的下落花了我2年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就選擇以堀田先生的生日派對作為你復仇的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還送了一張請帖給文子小姐是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子我在這個世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說沒有任何遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.14,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐不是已經開著車子安全離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一旦坐上了那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示我的復仇計畫已經成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在她的那輛車子裡動了手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只要用力踩刹車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會同時啟動駕駛座上的安全氣囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在恐怕已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確什麼都不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐到現在還是單身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為她到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是愛著健太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.32,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她這種連自己的父親都要趕她走的壞女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能這麼專一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是被趕出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是自己離開這個家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.47,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她沒辦法原諒自己的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對健太郎的所作所為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人明明拋棄了健太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.47,0:20:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是文子小姐的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珍藏著她對健太郎的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.82,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和思念的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是貼身戴著這條項鏈墜子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她心裡直到今天依然還愛著健太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.20,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩那麼深愛著我的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.12,0:20:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全氣囊沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.26,0:20:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生早就已經叫柯南把這件事告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要我假裝離開後再馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我這些年來一直在恨我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至想殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.97,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法原諒健太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把我一個人丟在這個世界上就離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓父親為他做這樣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個罪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良二先生原來被關在地下室了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.98,0:23:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.75,0:23:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子都快要餓扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.61,0:23:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也該吃早餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.14,0:23:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你把早餐拿來好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.40,0:23:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快餓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.14,0:23:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿來就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.87,0:23:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山內先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.70,0:23:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.60,0:23:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.70,0:24:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面膜不是應該在洗臉卸妝後再敷的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.88,0:24:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.32,0:24:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.52,0:24:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.19,0:24:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敷面膜殺人事件
